trans-unit.source: Represents a single HTTP header that is included in a response from the output cache.
trans-unit.target: 表示包含在从输出缓存响应的单个 HTTP 标头。

trans-unit.source: The HeaderElement class represents the content of an HTTP header in the output cache as a name/value pair.
trans-unit.target: HeaderElement 类作为名称/值对表示的 HTTP 标头输出缓存中的内容。

trans-unit.source: Both the name and the value must be non-null.
trans-unit.target: 名称和值必须为非 null。

trans-unit.source: The collection of all HeaderElement instances for an entry in the output cache is contained in the <xref:System.Web.Caching.IOutputCacheEntry.HeaderElements%2A> collection.
trans-unit.target: 中包含的输出缓存中的条目的所有 HeaderElement 实例的集合<xref:System.Web.Caching.IOutputCacheEntry.HeaderElements%2A>集合。</xref:System.Web.Caching.IOutputCacheEntry.HeaderElements%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Caching.HeaderElement"></xref> class.
When you create an instance of the <xref:System.Web.Caching.HeaderElement> class, the value of `name` must always be a non-null, non-empty string.
trans-unit.target: 当你创建的实例<xref:System.Web.Caching.HeaderElement>类的值`name`必须始终为非 null、 非空字符串。</xref:System.Web.Caching.HeaderElement>

trans-unit.source: The `value` parameter can be an empty string.
The name of the HTTP header.
The value of the HTTP header.
Gets the name of an HTTP header that is in the output cache.
trans-unit.target: 获取在输出缓存的 HTTP 标头的名称。

trans-unit.source: When you create an instance of the <xref:System.Web.Caching.HeaderElement> class, the value of `name` must always be a non-null, non-empty string.
trans-unit.target: 当你创建的实例<xref:System.Web.Caching.HeaderElement>类的值`name`必须始终为非 null、 非空字符串。</xref:System.Web.Caching.HeaderElement>

trans-unit.source: The name of the HTTP header.
Gets the value of an HTTP header that is in the output cache.
trans-unit.target: 获取在输出缓存的 HTTP 标头的值。

trans-unit.source: When you create an instance of the <xref:System.Web.Caching.HeaderElement> class, the `value` parameter can be an empty string.
trans-unit.target: 当你创建的实例<xref:System.Web.Caching.HeaderElement>类，`value`参数可以为空字符串。</xref:System.Web.Caching.HeaderElement>

trans-unit.source: The value of the HTTP header.
